author: Jordan B Peterson
description:
The newest course on Peterson Academy releases tonight at 8pm EST, Dr. Jordan Peterson's nine-hour course: Personality and Its Transformation.

In this course, Dr. Peterson presents a comprehensive exploration of personality psychology, integrating perspectives from psychoanalytic, humanistic, existential, and neurobiological traditions.

The lectures weave together insights from classical thinkers like Freud and Jung with modern psychological research, examining concepts such as the unconscious mind, personal transformation, and the role of dreams in psychological development.

Through discussions of the hero's journey, personality traits, and the integration of various psychological frameworks, the course offers a unified understanding of human personality development, combining ancient wisdom traditions with contemporary scientific findings to illuminate the processes of personal growth and transformation.

Enroll now and gain full access to all current and future Peterson Academy
title: Jordan Peterson’s Course: Personality and Its Transformation
